d fraud management services and community development and nonprofit services further the company provides wealth management services which comprise wealth accumulation protection and transfer services specialized services to institutional clients such as governments foundations corporations unions and nonprofit organizations corporate trust services and brokerage services in the areas of mutual funds fixed and variable annuities stocks bonds market linked cds unit investment trusts exchange traded funds and life insurance united bank inc was formerly known as united national bank and changed its name to united bank inc in march  the company was founded in  and is based in parkersburg west virginia with additional offices in west virginia ohio pennsylvania virginia maryland and washington dc united bank inc operates as a subsidiary of ubc holding company inc detailed description  market streetparkersburg wv united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwunitedbankwvcom key executives for united bank inc mr richard m adams chairman  ceo age  mr w mark tatterson chief financial officer and chief financial officer of united bankshares inc age  ms julie gurtis president of charleston market compensation as of fiscal year  united bank inc key developments marino j santarelli to leave from united financial bancorp inc and united bank as executive vice president and chief operating officer effective december   oct   united financial bancorp inc and united bank and marino j santarelli announced that they have agreed that santarelli will leave his positions at united primarily executive vice president and chief operating officer effective december   united intends to eliminate the chief operating officer position and has agreed to treat mr santarellis departure as a termination without cause under his employment agreement similar private companies by industry company name region  bancorp united states  bancorp mhc united states st financial bank usa united states st manatee bank uni